      <title>欧元区经济停滞，欧洲央行第五次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/ecb-cuts-rates-for-fifth-time-as-euro-zone-economy-flatlines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行自六月以来第五次下调借贷成本，而该地区经济陷入停滞，2%的通胀目标仍未实现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/ecb-cuts-rates-for-fifth-time-as-euro-zone-economy-flatlines</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 13:16:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消防局长称华盛顿空中坠机无人生还</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-30/no-survivors-in-midair-dc-crash-fire-chief-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国交通部长肖恩·达菲和华盛顿特区消防和急救部门负责人约翰·唐纳利在周三的简报会上就美国航空集团一架支线飞机与一架西科斯基 H-60 黑鹰军用直升机坠毁事件发表讲话。唐纳利局长表示：“目前，我们认为此次事故中无人幸存。”（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-30/no-survivors-in-midair-dc-crash-fire-chief-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 13:10:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗杰斯盈利超出预期，但 2025 年指引较弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/rogers-earnings-beat-expectations-but-guidance-weaker-for-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于无线服务收入增加且用户购买更昂贵的设备，罗杰斯通讯公司第四季度的业绩超出了分析师的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/rogers-earnings-beat-expectations-but-guidance-weaker-for-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 13:03:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
